caption:
Vulnerability is where true connection happens. 

At this year’s The Making Of Retreat, we opened up, shared our stories, and reminded ourselves that we’re stronger together. In a world that often celebrates perfection, it’s moments of honesty and authenticity that truly inspire growth.

When we allow ourselves to be vulnerable, we give others permission to do the same—and that’s where transformation begins. So thank you @ashleyjovesdds for always being willing to be vulnerable!

As we close out this year, let’s carry forward the courage to show up as our authentic selves, both in our businesses and in our lives.

What’s one way you’re embracing vulnerability as we move into 2025? We’d love to hear your thoughts.
